View our gallery

Our wedding floral package starts with the essentials, designed to bring your vision to life in a seamless, elegant way. The base package includes:

  • Bridal bouquet
  • Bridesmaids’ bouquets
  • Boutonnieres, corsages, and flower girl accessories
  • Ceremony floral arrangements (arch, aisle decor)
  • Reception centerpieces

Base Price: 1,200

Pricing Variables:

  • Guest Count: More guests may require additional tables, centerpieces, and decor.
  • Floral Selections: Premium or rare flowers may increase the overall cost.
  • Scale of Design: Larger installations or intricate floral designs (floral walls, suspended arrangements).
  • Venue Size/Logistics: Larger venues or locations requiring extended setup time may adjust the final pricing.

Pricing is tailored based on your unique vision.
